RainCaptcha,provides,anti,spam,protection,in,the,form,of,a,CAPTCHA,test,The,distorted,text,the,test,produces,is,designed,to,be,easy,for,people,to,read,but,hard,for,machines,to,decipher,RainCaptcha,requires,no,registration,and,is,free,for,both,personal,and,commercial,use,It,works,on,any,web,server,and,is,easy,to,implement,thanks,to,its,reliance,on,APIs,for,integration